title: Breaking Down Jalen's NBA Playoff Tiers
description:
Jalen & Jacoby bring you the post-All-Star NBA Playoff Tiers. Separating the contenders, hopefuls, question-marks, and wanna-be's from the East and West playoff picture. Who is in Jalen's Tier 1, where anything other than a title is a disappointment? Tune in to find out. PLUS! Jalen gives you a Larry Bird story that you absolutely do not want to miss. All that and more, tap in with J&J.
